{"tid":1087734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）醉漢誤扑15歲親女 承認強姦獲輕判","createTime":"2019-04-01T14:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T01:03:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85597389345e10d7f5ca6b55714bd4c1aca3761f","tid":1087734,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190401/large/1554110971_bb90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190401%2Flarge%2F1554110971_bb90.jpg&h=58f52d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年近六旬地盤工醉酒返家後，誤將15歲女兒當成妻子，在她不情願下強行性交，事後知道搞錯，十分懊悔。而妻子從女兒口中得知事件後，找社工幫忙，最後由社工報警。地盤工今於高等法院承認強姦罪，辯方向法庭呈上女兒在父親囚禁期間寫給父親的信，顯示她相信並原諒父親，亦未有因事件承受創傷，反而更積極面對人生。法官接納辯方求情，認為案情特殊，決定酌情減刑，判被告入獄2年10個月。<br />\n<br />\n現年59歲的被告於中國出生，1979年移居香港，與妻育有一子一女，長子正於英國求學。被告因心臟健康問題，需長期覆診服藥。他今早認罪，庭上未見其妻子或女兒旁聽。據悉，女兒在父親還柙期間，先後寫過10封信給父親，由家庭瑣事到自己最近看甚麼書、開始懂得體諒母親等等個人感受，都一一與父親分享。被告礙於候審身份，不能主動接觸證人，故一直未有回信。"},{"pid":"d996d9603bfb1e7f35381a937ec8f49c7d26d395","tid":1087734,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190401/59436739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190401%2F59436739&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=73320b40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190401%2F59436739&h=7bb670d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190401/59436739</a>"},{"pid":"03adada8119e2482249720ffc1adbf6e29fc84df","tid":1087734,"uid":142697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"啱咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93b8ea57d5b95ee7b5c2a9d141b235e98da54a5","tid":1087734,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"有人一早post左囉"},{"pid":"ebb90057805284dbd7458551fe153487b92e4e23","tid":1087734,"uid":174940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母   咁都原諒  個女弱智？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf2b8e864775b8861c1d418fb5318348c8e8c71","tid":1087734,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:03:53.000Z","msg":"點都估唔到係香港"}]}